You're Invited to Join <%= @company.name %>!

<%= @inviter.name %> has invited you to join <%= @company.name %> with the role of <%= @role.titleize %>.

<% case @role %>
<% when 'admin' %>
As an Admin, you'll have full access to all sites and can manage company settings.
<% when 'manager' %>
As a Manager, you'll have edit access to assigned sites and can create new sites.
<% when 'viewer' %>
As a Viewer, you'll have read-only access to assigned sites.
<% end %>

To accept your invitation, visit this link:
<%= @accept_url %>

This invitation will expire on <%= @expires_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>.

If you don't want to accept this invitation, you can simply ignore this email.

---
This invitation was sent by <%= @inviter.name %> from <%= @company.name %>.
If you have any questions, please contact your inviter directly.
